{"tid":90124,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做左10年地產狗,你問我答","createTime":"2017-01-21T19:29:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T15:59:16.000Z","uid":75148,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"05efa3f9b97255cc3502a8f824d8526361085efd","tid":90124,"uid":75148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T19:29:24.000Z","msg":"私人野唔答"},{"pid":"ba056b3b8e0fc6a1ed2fcf57e99141e77172a1b9","tid":90124,"uid":30055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T19:30:18.000Z","msg":"仲有冇得做"},{"pid":"fac25f0be075eb876850d65f26197417ac17cd35","tid":90124,"uid":75148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T19:30:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有冇得做</blockquote><br />\n冇"},{"pid":"3750d0621cef285acef1f63f4c399911e39b8551","tid":90124,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T19:31:13.000Z","msg":"你覺得你哋定係保險狗仆街啲"},{"pid":"8ccc767f0eaf4bf3b66e1c199a6fbc1f5c5c4a96","tid":90124,"uid":75148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T19:31:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你覺得你哋定係保險狗仆街啲</blockquote><br />\n一樣咁仆街,但兩每一行都有好人"},{"pid":"6b6c107d9b243937a97fd97edbec386cbf42ec4a","tid":90124,"uid":75148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T19:40:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你覺得你哋定係保險狗仆街啲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不過地產應該好少少,因為你始終真係有個實物係到"},{"pid":"4b3d2bf7bd25584b643e1743298b7be08365854d","tid":90124,"uid":75148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T19:42:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有冇得做</blockquote><br />\n其實地產由出左第一次辣招之後已經冇得做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88c2402b2311499b1eba1e924a2ad4659a4f9dfb","tid":90124,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T20:03:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f7da9db54c7280b9ff4850bb84dff68b20f3d184","tid":90124,"uid":75148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T20:12:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最貴一間幾錢，幾多佣金</blockquote><br />\n認真,最貴果間5300萬,客同業主共100萬佣,果陣自己開鋪唔洗分數比公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41e039241bad445d8a80182cff4c3f27cbf3bf2c","tid":90124,"uid":17474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T20:14:31.000Z","msg":"二手定新樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d5ffdb044c7dc2cdcce31b8e40d0f9405a66758","tid":90124,"uid":76959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T20:15:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>私人野唔答</blockquote><br />\n做邊區 我東區"},{"pid":"c6557d12596754a1afcc7bac03736dab6df6e001","tid":90124,"uid":75148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T20:17:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>二手定新樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n二手鋪"},{"pid":"929f71e7e508b194c454df53df64932536291b2d","tid":90124,"uid":75148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T20:18:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>私人野唔答</blockquote><br />\n做邊區 我東區</blockquote><br />\n新界"},{"pid":"859c16c1c8cdd86cdf6fe6041904213b27fff196","tid":90124,"uid":75148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T20:20:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>二手定新樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n二手鋪</blockquote><br />\n順帶一提間鋪持貨4年,銀行估價已8000萬up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3cf793c3cb843692ab7e022f5f980f75502dc6a","tid":90124,"uid":31591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T20:22:19.000Z","msg":"第一筒金點搵"},{"pid":"6a8b620a5030018d9a58ea38b45313fb4a12a2fd","tid":90124,"uid":2035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T20:22:45.000Z","msg":"宜家做緊乜？"},{"pid":"aaf2003992d88a00a5d9ad197792ca56a56c23ad","tid":90124,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T20:25:21.000Z","msg":"10年一共揾咗幾錢 約數"},{"pid":"46fe6761d46e1842ec55d6911547516e4b164a53","tid":90124,"uid":75148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T20:26:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一筒金點搵</blockquote><br />\n當年仲可以摩貨年代,地產經紀會摩埋一份,叻既地產經紀一日可以執十幾萬(當然依加冇得摩貨啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"ee82d888443ac8a80289c5720f94e93ea2025bcb","tid":90124,"uid":75148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T20:26:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>宜家做緊乜？</blockquote><br />\n做緊...收租佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c787e994ebfb87ea79ecdfd96cd283b421b85c26","tid":90124,"uid":31591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T20:28:01.000Z","msg":"好撚妒忌"},{"pid":"178b7d920af9c15f616ba2c48f5cb00a771d6637","tid":90124,"uid":75148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T20:28:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>10年一共揾咗幾錢 約數</blockquote><br />\n我講完一定有人話我吹水,信就信,唔信就算...不打算証明<br />\n<br />\n800萬左右"},{"pid":"81469fabae30a7983f75d1c79fb6a6ef59698a1f","tid":90124,"uid":75148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T20:29:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好撚妒忌</blockquote><br />\n只能說...時勢做英雄,而加你見到既地產仔十個有九個都等餓死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e00ca65d22c07614b865d402b5436a75fd542695","tid":90124,"uid":44460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T20:31:31.000Z","msg":"駿景園, 帝寶 大單位你會點揀?(要埋車位)<br />\nBtw, 我都識個地產佬而家揸住十層樓收租"},{"pid":"07f6d4fde532510c39ec7375168351c4bdfc3c5a","tid":90124,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T20:33:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb9b1fd9d987b63d85db24a3db98770a34b0f5c","tid":90124,"uid":75148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T20:37:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>駿景園, 帝寶 大單位你會點揀?(要埋車位)<br />\nBtw, 我都識個地產佬而家揸住十層樓收租</blockquote><br />\n唔係太熟沙田,但要揀應該會揀駿景,我記得帝堡好似係深山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老一輩既老產佬㨁住十層樓真係唔出奇...大有人在,因為果陣可以做9成半按揭,其實拎好少首期出黎,之後租客供,再加埋樓價升幅真係唔難..."},{"pid":"224327f8149a61b783d6dc13afc518b13e325254","tid":90124,"uid":75148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T20:38:34.000Z","msg":"唔好意思,手機出字,成日打錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3114a2d9a1b7cfc27f4d2f23d54ab452ab3dfb32","tid":90124,"uid":31591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T20:40:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好撚妒忌</blockquote><br />\n只能說...時勢做英雄,而加你見到既地產仔十個有九個都等餓死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大約幾耐開一張單"},{"pid":"cdfedd191d9663cd3404560e4852d0e12d84c762","tid":90124,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T20:41:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>10年一共揾咗幾錢 約數</blockquote><br />\n我講完一定有人話我吹水,信就信,唔信就算...不打算証明<br />\n<br />\n800萬左右</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n信 因為10年揾800萬真係唔多..."},{"pid":"7fef85dc5983cf158992d7a32fdc472438743db6","tid":90124,"uid":62318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T20:43:51.000Z","msg":"盧<blockquote><blockquote>宜家做緊乜？</blockquote><br />\n做緊...收租佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪姐係好似大富翁咁，乜都唔洗做，每個月收租就已經多個D打工仔既人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係度享受世界，咁樣真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15c318b4f69192ec4b883b1c845dc4995ee4ba52","tid":90124,"uid":75148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T20:44:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好撚妒忌</blockquote><br />\n只能說...時勢做英雄,而加你見到既地產仔十個有九個都等餓死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大約幾耐開一張單</blockquote><br />\n以後有得摩貨既年代,一日最過記錄係23單買賣<br />\n依加...勤力既話一個月平均3-4單"},{"pid":"07237c10578d9f0c40aa800891313017dbb08f39","tid":90124,"uid":75148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T20:45:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>盧<blockquote><blockquote>宜家做緊乜？</blockquote><br />\n做緊...收租佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪姐係好似大富翁咁，乜都唔洗做，每個月收租就已經多個D打工仔既人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係度享受世界，咁樣真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而加揸住8層樓,平均每間收緊1萬,但係有4間都仲供緊"},{"pid":"9a87db21e8e11e97ec732fe33332b3594f166504","tid":90124,"uid":75148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T20:47:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>10年一共揾咗幾錢 約數</blockquote><br />\n我講完一定有人話我吹水,信就信,唔信就算...不打算証明<br />\n<br />\n800萬左右</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n信 因為10年揾800萬真係唔多...</blockquote><br />\n800萬係佣金收入,未計當年摩貨炒樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:未夠30歲"},{"pid":"c05ab883c8e8aa41efd54795a6c3d8612056b19e","tid":90124,"uid":44460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T20:49:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>駿景園, 帝寶 大單位你會點揀?(要埋車位)<br />\nBtw, 我都識個地產佬而家揸住十層樓收租</blockquote><br />\n唔係太熟沙田,但要揀應該會揀駿景,我記得帝堡好似係深山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老一輩既老產佬㨁住十層樓真係唔出奇...大有人在,因為果陣可以做9成半按揭,其實拎好少首期出黎,之後租客供,再加埋樓價升幅真係唔難...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n乜咁早！多謝你意見先<br />\n呢兩個地方連盤都好少 我睇左成年都冇啱心水(主要係自己供唔起) <br />\n而家香港人, 自問自己收入可以, 不過買樓真係好撚麻煩 <br />\n唉，佢四十中到,  佢一買就租比人 佢真係十年到就已經有十層 因為佢本身住我附近平時有兩句水吹所以知."},{"pid":"4f1b9acebfaa067a18247ff8683adf057527a8f9","tid":90124,"uid":75148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T20:55:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>駿景園, 帝寶 大單位你會點揀?(要埋車位)<br />\nBtw, 我都識個地產佬而家揸住十層樓收租</blockquote><br />\n唔係太熟沙田,但要揀應該會揀駿景,我記得帝堡好似係深山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老一輩既老產佬㨁住十層樓真係唔出奇...大有人在,因為果陣可以做9成半按揭,其實拎好少首期出黎,之後租客供,再加埋樓價升幅真係唔難...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n乜咁早！多謝你意見先<br />\n呢兩個地方連盤都好少 我睇左成年都冇啱心水(主要係自己供唔起) <br />\n而家香港人, 自問自己收入可以, 不過買樓真係好撚麻煩 <br />\n唉，佢四十中到,  佢一買就租比人 佢真係十年到就已經有十層 因為佢本身住我附近平時有兩句水吹所以知.</blockquote><br />\n認真,依加個樓價...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地做地產既都覺得個價真係好癲,但冇辦法幾癲都係有人接貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n至於你話麻煩...真係多撚謝689條仆街...親眼見有好多後生仔係比佢搞到上唔到車,想知再講...<br />\n我而加揸住8間,但有啲仲供緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e58109bf59b7e3bdf076a51c5ba398c333b4097","tid":90124,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T20:58:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4d46fb49762afc3bb5f22e8cf5cb18057005fe62","tid":90124,"uid":75148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T20:59:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>吹到自己係神童輝咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔鐘意親負皮然後上一頁啦"},{"pid":"44ecfc05dee89f5315ca7c0dc30a86b9a09dd456","tid":90124,"uid":51678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T20:59:40.000Z","msg":"依個年代二十出頭無父幹要點上樓？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6c8849147048c41d44a74de4767de1421153e2f","tid":90124,"uid":6666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T21:01:41.000Z","msg":"樓主好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家讀緊大學就出黎做野 樓價雖然好癲但係咪如果想有間屋企都唯有硬食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"717d574ced2bc2253f205b735716b4b40f99321f","tid":90124,"uid":75148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T21:05:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依個年代二十出頭無父幹要點上樓？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認真,真係好難...由細碼樓入手啦(唔好買新果啲劏房,幾多條命都唔夠你死),九成按揭,然後樓換樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n至於果一成首期...自求多福"},{"pid":"1ffb8e4742796d52c22c0e3a0ae102d4714f8301","tid":90124,"uid":75148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T21:06:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家讀緊大學就出黎做野 樓價雖然好癲但係咪如果想有間屋企都唯有硬食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔勁...好彩啫,中五畢業,會考0分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比心機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8668856a67a0f1c29cce65b28fe9cfd254c4045","tid":90124,"uid":75148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T21:07:24.000Z","msg":"0分好似叫修業<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a251b4db2673aa1c51382c664d059cdebdaa3c6","tid":90124,"uid":25797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T21:34:27.000Z","msg":"點睇著西裝通街 R人睇樓個班"},{"pid":"90b23583d8bef9ae093f389625527ab75ee49fe1","tid":90124,"uid":75148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T21:37:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點睇著西裝通街 R人睇樓個班</blockquote><br />\n垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n影衰地產"},{"pid":"6f778bd9272da4424bab13d1170f9a2b201fcb34","tid":90124,"uid":75148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T21:38:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點睇著西裝通街 R人睇樓個班</blockquote><br />\n下次見到請報EAA,因為大多數都係冇牌"},{"pid":"fb5c4de132efcc284bc7ffad1382b29fa2dfd829","t