oji\" />"},{"pid":"6ec98cd46513f669abb80a1cbc15bade965b4aad","tid":90124,"uid":77332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T14:15:41.000Z","msg":"扯旗爸打有無telegram想問下有乜盤推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}